ith the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n         \u003C/surface>\n    \u003C/facsimile>\n    \u003Ctext>\n        \u003Cbody>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"edition\" subtype=\"primary\" xml:space=\"preserve\" xml:lang=\"la\" resp=\"#JP\">\n                \u003Cab>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"1\"/>Cornelio Masu\u003Csupplied reason=\"omitted\">e\u003C/supplied>to\n                    \u003Clb n=\"2\"/>\u003CroleName type=\"supracivic\" subtype=\"procurator\">\u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>procurat\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>ori\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan>\u003C/roleName>  \u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>Ti\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>berii\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan> \u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>Caesar\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>is\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"3\"/>\u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>Aug\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>usti\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan> et Iuliae \u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>August\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>ae\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"4\"/>ex \u003CroleName type=\"civic\" subtype=\"decurio\">\u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>d\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>ecurionum\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan>\u003C/roleName> \u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>d\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>ecreto\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan> \u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>p\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>ecunia\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan> \u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>p\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>ublica\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan>\n                \u003C/ab>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"apparatus\">\n                \u003ClistApp>\u003Capp>\u003Cnote>Text of I.Lipara\u003C/note>\u003C/app>\u003C/listApp>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"translation\">\n                \u003Cp>\u003C!--translation(s) - add @xml:lang for 'en' or 'it' to div-->\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"commentary\">\n                \u003Cp>\u003C!--commented out pending revision-->\n                    \u003C!--in BTCGI, p.101: 'L'iscrizione di Cornelio Masuto (?) procurator Tiberii Caesaris Augusti et Iuliae Augustae vista da Gualtherius dinanzi alla cattedrale di S. Bartolomeo (Mommsen 1883 nr.7489) fece favoleggiare l'esistenza di latifondi imperiali a chi non si rendeva conto che l'isola misura Km.9 x 4 ed e per piu di meta incoltivabile. Ci si potrebbe chiedere se questo procuraor non fosse per caso il gestoredelle cave di allume e di zolfo ricordate da Diodoro e da Strabone come una delle principali risorse dell'isla, da cui i Romani e i Liparesi traevano notevoli proventi'.-->\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"bibliography\">\n                \u003ClistBibl type=\"edition\">\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"corpus\" n=\"CIL\">\n                        \u003Cauthor>Mommsen\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1883\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>\n                            \u003Cref target=\"http://arachne.uni-koeln.de/books/CILv10pII1883\">7489\u003C/ref>\n                        \u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/GQN8UZSI\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"corpus\" n=\"ILipara\">\n \u2028                        \u003Cauthor>Bernabó-Brea\u003C/author>\n \u2028                        \u003Cauthor>Cavalier\u003C/author>\n \u2028                        \u003Cauthor>Campagna\u003C/author>\n \u2028                        \u003Cdate>2003\u003C/date> \n                        \u003CcitedRange>756\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/VDAQH5D2\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000541\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000541\u00